course.subject: ENGG
course.name: Robotics Special Project: RoboGames 2024 & SmartCar Challenge
course.description: The RoboGames is an international competition for young engineers. Student teams will design and manufacture racing model car for tackling different missions and challenges which are provided by the organizer. SmartCar Challenge is a national competition held in late July to August. Student teams will design a programmable car and to completed with other school teams. Normally, a project report is required. Enrollment in the project course may require instructor's approval. May be graded PP.
